		<title>Through the Work of More than 60 Artists, ‘The Golden Thread’ Traces the Rise of Textiles in Contemporary Art</title>
		<link>https://www.sawberries.com/2024/05/07/the-golden-thread-fiber-art/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ross]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 21:01:17 +0000</pubDate>
