</div>
<div id="attachment_246997" style="width: 1930px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-246997" class="wp-image-246997 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/thread-3.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1435" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/thread-3.jpg 1920w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/thread-3-640x478.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/thread-3-960x718.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/thread-3-1536x1148.jpg 1536w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/thread-3-285x214.jpg 285w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px"></p>
<p id="caption-attachment-246997" class="wp-caption-text">Melissa Webb, “Manifestoon” (2024), hand-dyed and manipulated vintage cotton textiles, site-responsive installation, dimensions variable</p>
</div>
<div id="attachment_246999" style="width: 1930px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-246999" class="wp-image-246999 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/thread-5.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1440" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/thread-5.jpg 1920w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/thread-5-640x480.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/thread-5-960x720.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/thread-5-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/thread-5-285x214.jpg 285w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px"></p>
<p id="caption-attachment-246999" class="wp-caption-text">Jeila Gueramian, “It Reminds Me of You” (2024), mixed media, site-specific, dimensions variable</p>
</div>
<div id="attachment_247001" style="width: 1930px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-247001" class="wp-image-247001 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/thread-7.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1308" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/thread-7.jpg 1920w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/thread-7-640x436.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/thread-7-960x654.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/thread-7-1536x1046.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px"></p>
<p id="caption-attachment-247001" class="wp-caption-text">Erin LeAnn Mitchell, “Equally Yoked” (2024), acrylic, fabric, buttons, yarns and loop hair rollers, 60 x 40 inches</p>
</div>
<div id="attachment_246995" style="width: 1683px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-246995" class="wp-image-246995 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/thread-1.jpg" alt="" width="1673" height="1920" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/thread-1.jpg 1673w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/thread-1-640x734.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/thread-1-960x1102.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/thread-1-1338x1536.jpg 1338w" sizes="(max-width: 1673px) 100vw, 1673px"></p>
<p id="caption-attachment-246995" class="wp-caption-text">Sarah Zapata, “A Famine of Hearing (Green Ruins 1-4)” (2019), natural and synthetic fiber, wood, dimensions variable</p>
</div>
